# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-15 14:26

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:9
translate chinese day1_f277ad4a:

    # "THE NEXT MORNING"
    "第二天早上"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:14
translate chinese day1_140f51d4:

    # "I am woken by a knock on my door."
    "我被敲门声吵醒了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:15
translate chinese day1_d72509a6:

    # pc "Yeah?"
    pc "什么事？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:16
translate chinese day1_1b92974a:

    # sp "I made breakfast. You have a little time to eat before you need to go register for school."
    sp "我做了早餐。你去学校注册前还有点时间吃。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:17
translate chinese day1_836b3b51:

    # "I look around, disoriented for a moment. It takes a bit for me to realize where I am – in my bedroom, at home."
    "我环顾四周，一时有些茫然。过了好一会儿我才意识到自己身在何处——在家里的卧室里。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:18
translate chinese day1_71d014f3:

    # "I had fallen asleep hard the night before and didn't wake up at all throughout the night. Unusual for me."
    "昨晚我睡得很沉，整晚都没醒过。这对我来说很不寻常。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:19
translate chinese day1_84e65c22:

    # pc "Okay, thanks. I'll be down in a few minutes. "
    pc "好的，谢谢。我几分钟后就下去。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:20
translate chinese day1_9f064b85:

    # sp "I have to get to work. I won't be home until late tonight. Have a good day."
    sp "我得去上班了。今晚很晚才能回家。祝你今天过得愉快。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:21
translate chinese day1_790762a2:

    # "I crawl out of bed, feeling pretty good. The clock on my nightstand says it is 9:15. "
    "我爬出床，感觉挺不错的。床头柜上的钟显示现在是9点15分。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:23
translate chinese day1_cdbaf5ac:

    # "I give a little knock on the bathroom door to make sure that Suzy isn't in there, then walk in, empty my bladder, and smooth out my bedhead a bit. "
    "我轻轻敲了敲浴室门，确认苏茜不在里面，然后走了进去，解决完生理需求，顺便把睡乱的头发整理了一下。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:26
translate chinese day1_b945239f:

    # "Then I throw a shirt on and head downstairs, where I can smell pancakes before I even get to the bottom step. "
    "接着我套上件衬衫下楼，还没走到最后一级台阶，就已经闻到了煎饼的香味。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:29
translate chinese day1_e9b07aab:

    # "Suzy is already sitting at the table eating. "
    "苏茜已经坐在餐桌前吃早餐了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:30
translate chinese day1_bb51adeb:

    # ss "The pancakes are under the foil in there. "
    ss "煎饼就在那里的锡纸下面。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:31
translate chinese day1_b53f8364:

    # pc "Thanks. "
    pc "谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:34
translate chinese day1_d1f6cf0b:

    # "I go to the kitchen and put two pancakes on my plate along with a pad of butter and a little syrup, then I walk back to the dining room and sit across from Suzy."
    "我走进厨房，在盘子里放了两块煎饼，配上一小块黄油和一点糖浆，然后走回餐厅，坐在苏茜对面。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:35
translate chinese day1_4025fcb1:

    # ss "She hasn't cooked breakfast in forever. I'm not sure why you're getting the special treatment, but I'm happy for the pancakes. "
    ss "她已经很久没做早餐了。我不清楚你为什么能享受这种特殊待遇，但能吃到煎饼我还是很开心的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:36
translate chinese day1_7a4286af:

    # pc "Careful. It almost sounded like you were saying that you're happy I'm back. "
    pc "小心点。你这话听起来好像是在说，你很高兴我回来了。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:38
translate chinese day1_7edc6e89:

    # ss "Are you back? Or are you just going to leave us again? "
    ss "你回来了？还是又要离开我们？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:39
translate chinese day1_62e06f66:

    # pc "I'm back. Seriously. I'm not going anywhere. "
    pc "我回来了。真的。我不会再走了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:41
translate chinese day1_d9d7dc1b:

    # "Suzy scoffs, unconvinced. "
    "苏茜不以为然地嗤笑一声。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:42
translate chinese day1_aefae29f:

    # ss "We'll see. "
    ss "走着瞧。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:43
translate chinese day1_7a69dfe1:

    # pc "I promise, [sis]. Really. I'm not going back. You're going to have to deal with me for a long time. "
    pc "我保证，[sis]。真的。我不会回去了。你们得长期忍受我了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:45
translate chinese day1_1d417bec:

    # "Suzy smiles, side-eyeing me."
    "苏茜瞥了我一眼，笑了笑。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:46
translate chinese day1_85c4dd14:

    # ss "Great. "
    ss "太好了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:47
translate chinese day1_51120906:

    # ss "I'm going to go get ready. Be ready at 10, okay? "
    ss "我去准备一下。10点准时出发，行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:48
translate chinese day1_fc94baf7:

    # pc "You got it. And thanks for being my ride for today. "
    pc "没问题。谢谢你今天送我一程。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:49
translate chinese day1_971e823a:

    # ss "Yeah, just don't make it a habit. "
    ss "行，但别养成习惯。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:52
translate chinese day1_9f8d7627:

    # "She stands up and grabs her plate, heading towards the kitchen. "
    "她站起身拿起盘子，走向厨房。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:53
translate chinese day1_e0bc8a6d:

    # pc "Hey, [sis]? "
    pc "嘿，[sis]？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:54
translate chinese day1_4339758a:

    # ss "What? "
    ss "怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:55
translate chinese day1_13248281:

    # pc "When's trash day? "
    pc "什么时候收垃圾？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:56
translate chinese day1_33714114:

    # ss "How the hell should I know? Friday maybe? "
    ss "我怎么知道？周五吧？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:57
translate chinese day1_c4b1d53a:

    # pc "So today?"
    pc "所以是今天？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:58
translate chinese day1_751e4576:

    # ss "Maybe?"
    ss "也许吧？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:59
translate chinese day1_87647b2c:

    # "I think about asking her to help me take the trash out, but then decide against it. Easier to just do it by myself. "
    "我本想让她帮我把垃圾拿出去，但转念一想还是算了。自己动手更省事。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:60
translate chinese day1_775dea27:

    # "I eat quickly, scarfing down all the delicious pancakes. Then I put my plate into the sink before grabbing the kitchen trash and carrying it outside to the trash bins. "
    "我狼吞虎咽地吃着，把那些美味的煎饼全吃光了。 随后我把盘子放进水槽，拿起厨房的垃圾桶，把它扛到屋外扔进垃圾箱。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:63
translate chinese day1_f4cc524d:

    # "It takes two trips to move the trash cans to the curb and I get them there just as the garbage man is driving up to the house to pick them up. "
    "我来回跑了两趟才把垃圾桶搬到路边，刚把它们放好，垃圾车就开到了门口准备收走。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:64
translate chinese day1_3e905c90:

    # "He gives me a wave and a smile before I realize that I had never put on pants and am standing outside in my boxers. Oops."
    "他向我挥手微笑，这时我才意识到自己根本没穿裤子，正光着一条内裤站在外面。哎呀。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:66
translate chinese day1_aa42da63:

    # "I rush back inside and upstairs, throwing on some clothes from my suitcase and making a quick trip to the bathroom to make myself a bit more presentable. "
    "我匆忙跑回屋里上楼，从行李箱里随便抓了件衣服套上，又匆匆跑进浴室稍微打理了一下，让自己看起来像样些。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:67
translate chinese day1_481ad73c:

    # "When I'm finished, it is exactly 10 a.m."
    "等我弄好时，正好是上午10点。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:68
translate chinese day1_f2bae43e:

    # ss "Alright, [bro], let's go!"
    ss "好了，[bro]，走吧！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:72
translate chinese day1_caf40c4b:

    # "She calls from the front door. I make sure I have everything I need, then rush down the stairs to meet her at the front door."
    "她从前门喊道。我确认带齐了所有必需品，随即冲下楼梯，在前门和她会合。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:73
translate chinese day1_1660493b:

    # pc "Ready!"
    pc "准备好了！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:76
translate chinese day1_7072f207:

    # "She leads me out to her car, an older model SUV. The interior is messy with empty coffee cups and fast food bags. I sit in the passenger seat and buckle up."
    "她带我走到她的车旁，是一辆老款SUV。车内乱糟糟的，到处都是空咖啡杯和快餐袋。我坐进副驾驶座系好安全带。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:79
translate chinese day1_365fcfce:

    # pc "This feels weird. "
    pc "这感觉真怪。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:80
translate chinese day1_4339758a_1:

    # ss "What? "
    ss "怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:81
translate chinese day1_63cbd288:

    # pc "You driving. Remember all the times I had to drive you places when we were growing up? "
    pc "你开车。还记得我们小时候，我总得开车带你去各种地方吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:82
translate chinese day1_722468e6:

    # ss "Yeah, but I'm not a kid anymore. And you're not driving my car. "
    ss "是啊，但我已经不是小孩了。而且你也没开我的车。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:83
translate chinese day1_c9e546cd:

    # pc "I'm just saying it's weird. "
    pc "我只是觉得有点怪。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:86
translate chinese day1_4a97b04a:

    # ss "Alright, let's get this show on the road."
    ss "行啦，咱们上路吧。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:89
translate chinese day1_a30cda1c:

    # "She backs out without looking into the rearview mirror, then slams down on the brakes, jerking me forward in my seat. "
    "她倒车时连后视镜都没看，随后猛踩刹车，把我整个人往前甩去。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:92
translate chinese day1_e947ee1f:

    # "She shifts up into drive and then puts the gas pedal to the floor."
    "她挂上D挡，随即把油门踩到底。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:93
translate chinese day1_5c62a101:

    # "I grip the dashboard, holding on for my life as she zooms down the side streets, barely slowing around corners. "
    "我死死抓住仪表盘，拼命抓紧，她飞驰在小巷里，过弯时几乎不减速。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:94
translate chinese day1_9bfb97be:

    # "It only takes a few minutes to get to the school. "
    "到学校只用了几分钟。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:99
translate chinese day1_fc69d3c6:

    # ss "The counselor's office is over there. I'm going to the café over there to have a drink and chat with a friend. Just come get me when you're done. "
    ss "辅导员的办公室在那边。我要去那边的咖啡馆喝点东西，跟朋友聊聊天。你办完事就来接我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:100
translate chinese day1_06d3bcbf:

    # pc "Okay, thanks. "
    pc "好的，谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:101
translate chinese day1_bc7ca1a4:

    # ss "And don't take all day either. I have things I want to do later. "
    ss "别花一整天时间。我下午还有事要做。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:102
translate chinese day1_f75c9919:

    # pc "I'll try. "
    pc "我会尽量的。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:105
translate chinese day1_51bf71a6:

    # "I walk through the courtyard towards the administration office that Suzy had pointed to. "
    "我穿过庭院，朝苏西指给我的行政办公室走去。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:106
translate chinese day1_e42a8d36:

    # "The lobby is busy with people. All students looking to register, like me. "
    "大厅里人来人往，忙碌非凡。所有学生都像我一样，是来办理注册手续的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:107
translate chinese day1_b72f9460:

    # "I sign in at the front desk, then wait for my turn to talk to a counselor. "
    "我在前台签到，然后等着轮到我与辅导员交谈。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:108
translate chinese day1_c607938a:

    # "It takes nearly an hour for my name to be called. The young woman at the front desk leads me down a short hall and knocks on a partially opened door with a nameplate that says Gertrude Spann."
    "足足等了近一个小时，才轮到我。前台那位年轻女子领我穿过一条短走廊，敲了敲一扇半开的门，门牌上写着“格特鲁德·斯潘”。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:109
translate chinese day1_793493ec:

    # "Assistant" "The next student is here, Mrs. Spann."
    "Assistant" "“斯潘夫人，下一位学生到了。”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:114
translate chinese day1_f67002ce:

    # sc "Thank you. Hello there, you can just call me Gertrude. It's nice to meet you."
    sc "“谢谢。你好，你可以直接叫我格特鲁德。很高兴见到你。”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:115
translate chinese day1_6312d9da:

    # "She puts her hand out to shake mine, gripping it firmly for only a second, then sitting back into her chair and motioning for me to sit across from her."
    "她伸出手与我握手，只紧握了一秒钟，随即坐回椅子上，示意我坐在她对面。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:118
translate chinese day1_d1a3cf1a:

    # "The assistant quickly walks back towards the front desk to help the next student in line. "
    "助理迅速走回前台，去接待排在队列中的下一位学生。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:119
translate chinese day1_0d80bf66:

    # sc "So what are we doing today? "
    sc "“那么，我们今天要办什么事？”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:120
translate chinese day1_285035ca:

    # pc "I need to register. I've been going to a college in Brazil for the last three years, but I want to transfer here to finish my degree. "
    pc "“我想办理注册手续。过去三年我一直在巴西的一所大学就读，但我想转学到这里完成学业。” "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:122
translate chinese day1_371df839:

    # sc "Brazil? Wow! What were you going to school there for? "
    sc "“巴西？哇！你在那里读什么专业？”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:123
translate chinese day1_75cc0f72:

    # pc "I had a full scholarship studying quantum physics. "
    pc "“我拿到了全额奖学金，主修量子物理。”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:124
translate chinese day1_f5dc9bb8:

    # sc "That's amazing! What happened? Why didn't you finish your degree there, if you don't mind me asking? "
    sc "“太棒了！发生了什么事？如果可以问的话，你为什么没在那里完成学业？”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:125
translate chinese day1_36677773:

    # pc "I came home to help with my family. My dad went missing a few weeks ago and we're trying to find him. I felt like I needed to come home."
    pc "“我回国是来帮家里忙的。几周前我爸爸失踪了，我们正在找他。我觉得我必须回家。”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:127
translate chinese day1_349dc86a:

    # sc "Oh, I understand. I hope you find your dad, that's awful. "
    sc "哦，我明白了。希望你能找到你爸爸，这太糟糕了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:128
translate chinese day1_92507930:

    # pc "Thank you. "
    pc "谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:130
translate chinese day1_b1340b73:

    # sc "Okay, so you want to finish your degree here. I'm assuming a BS in Physics first, then we'll look at the Masters and Doctorate programs afterwards. "
    sc "好的，所以你想在这里完成学业。我猜你先要拿个物理学学士学位，之后我们再考虑硕士和博士项目。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:131
translate chinese day1_e9630f89:

    # sc "You said you took three years in Brazil. Do you have the official transcripts? "
    sc "你说你在巴西读了三年。你有正式的成绩单吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:132
translate chinese day1_68b34aac:

    # pc "Yes, I brought them with me. "
    pc "是的，我带过来了。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:133
translate chinese day1_68acff9f:

    # "I hand her the transcripts and she looks them over with a frown on her face."
    "我把成绩单递给她，她皱着眉头翻看了起来。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:135
translate chinese day1_f65849f0:

    # sc "Okay, okay. Yeah, these look good, but you're missing a couple of basic education courses. "
    sc "好的，好的。嗯，这些看起来不错，但你缺了几门基础教育课程。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:136
translate chinese day1_cb515ed6:

    # pc "Basic education? "
    pc "基础教育？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:138
translate chinese day1_aebbf4f9:

    # sc "Yes, for your degree, you're required to have one semester in English and one in Social Studies. You don't have those here. "
    sc "是的，要获得学位，你必须修满一个学期的英语和一个学期的社会研究课程。你这里没有这些课程。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:139
translate chinese day1_fad16ea5:

    # pc "It wasn't required at my other college. We were completely focused on Science. "
    pc "我之前那所大学没要求这些。我们完全专注于理科。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:140
translate chinese day1_9b9e7d7e:

    # sc "That makes sense, but you'll have to take them here. You'll be close to having your BS after taking them though, since you've already taken some of the more intense Science classes. "
    sc "这可以理解，但你必须在这里补修。不过修完这些后，你离拿到理学学士学位就不远了，毕竟你已经修过一些难度较高的理科课程。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:141
translate chinese day1_833a138b:

    # sc "Do you want to take a full course load? If you do, I can probably easily get you into a scholarship program considering your current situation. "
    sc "你想修满全额学分吗？如果想的话，考虑到你目前的状况，我应该能轻松帮你申请到奖学金。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:142
translate chinese day1_ae785278:

    # "A full course load would be a lot of work, but I need to get it done. Plus, I don't have the money to pay for college on my own. I need a scholarship of some sort. "
    "修满全额学分工作量会很大，但我必须完成。而且，我没有钱自己支付大学学费。我需要某种形式的奖学金。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:143
translate chinese day1_2289f1ba:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do that. "
    pc "好的，那就这么办。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:144
translate chinese day1_fcf730d7:

    # sc "Okay, so I'll sign you up for this scholarship. We'll know for sure in a week whether you're qualified or not, but I'm pretty sure you will be fine. "
    sc "好的，那我就帮你申请这个奖学金。一周后就能确定你是否符合条件，但我相信你肯定没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:145
translate chinese day1_a28b07e0:

    # sc "And I'm going to register you for your classes – you'll take English and Social Studies, along with the rest of the science classes that you need. You should be good to graduate by the end of the semester."
    sc "我还会帮你选课——你会修英语和社会研究，外加其他必修的科学课程。这样你应该能在本学期结束前顺利毕业。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:146
translate chinese day1_23804ef9:

    # sc "It's a big course load, but most people don't have any problem with these classes. I think with your previous experience and obvious intellect, you will be fine. "
    sc "虽然课业负担挺重，但大多数学生上这些课都没什么问题。我觉得以你的过往经验和显而易见的聪慧，你肯定没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:147
translate chinese day1_1704862e:

    # pc "That sounds great. "
    pc "听起来很棒。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:148
translate chinese day1_bac5ae79:

    # sc "Let me get your ID and I'll take these transcripts and get started. "
    sc "请把你的身份证给我，我拿这些成绩单去办理。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:150
translate chinese day1_f9ff879e:

    # "I hand her my ID from my wallet, then wait while she types up some things at the computer. "
    "我从钱包里掏出身份证递给她，然后等着她用电脑输入一些信息。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:151
translate chinese day1_cdba79e3:

    # "Then she prints off some pages, has me sign a few places, and hands me a large folder stuffed full of papers. "
    "随后她打印了几页文件，让我在几处签字，然后递给我一个塞得满满当当的大文件夹。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:153
translate chinese day1_bf9053dc:

    # sc "Okay, everything's done. "
    sc "好了，一切都搞定了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:154
translate chinese day1_60d1bbaf:

    # sc "In your folder there, you'll find your schedule, your course plan, and some more information you might find useful about the school. "
    sc "那个文件夹里有你的课表、课程计划，还有一些关于学校的有用信息。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:155
translate chinese day1_061a7bd6:

    # sc "Your scholarship is all set up and seems to be good. You just need to show up on Monday ready to go."
    sc "你的奖学金已经办妥，看起来没问题。你只需要周一准时到校报到就行。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:156
translate chinese day1_8cadbc6f:

    # pc "Wow, that was easy. Thank you. "
    pc "哇，真简单。谢谢你。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:157
translate chinese day1_a4e55d91:

    # sc "And feel free to come up and chat with me if you ever need anything. Usually the place is not nearly this busy and you shouldn't have to wait long to see me."
    sc "如果你有什么需要，随时可以来找我聊聊。通常这里没这么忙，你不用等太久就能见到我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:158
translate chinese day1_b93e3840:

    # sc "It doesn't have to be school related. I'm a counselor and I'm here to help you succeed in any way I can. "
    sc "不一定要是学校相关的事。我是辅导员，我就在这里，尽我所能帮助你取得成功。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:159
translate chinese day1_74f006d8:

    # sc "And good luck finding your dad. I hope everything turns out okay. "
    sc "祝你找到你爸爸。希望一切都能顺利。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:160
translate chinese day1_514b6719:

    # pc "Thank you so much. "
    pc "非常感谢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:161
translate chinese day1_fb3340fa:

    # "She shakes my hand one more time before I leave and walk back down through the busy lobby and out into the courtyard once again. "
    "在我离开前，她又和我握了一次手。我穿过熙熙攘攘的大厅，再次走出了庭院。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:164
translate chinese day1_340e82bc:

    # "I make my way over towards the café that Suzy had pointed towards earlier. "
    "我朝苏茜刚才指给我的那家咖啡馆走去。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:165
translate chinese day1_606a8b00:

    # "Through the glass window, I can see Suzy sitting at a table, leaning back with her feet propped up in another chair, staring idly at her telephone screen. "
    "透过玻璃窗，我看到苏茜正坐在一张桌子旁，靠在椅背上，双脚搭在另一把椅子上，漫不经心地盯着手机屏幕。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:167
translate chinese day1_55c29a9d:

    # "A bell on the door gives a little ring as I walk in. Some students glance up at me from an area to the right where they sit in comfortable looking couches and bean bag chairs, but most pay me no attention. "
    "我推门而入时，门上的铃铛叮地响了一声。右侧区域里，几个学生从看起来很舒适的沙发和豆袋椅上抬眼瞥了我一眼，但大多数人根本没理会我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:169
translate chinese day1_9a5ad86a:

    # ss "It's about time. I was so BORED, and my phone is almost dead. "
    ss "你总算来了。我无聊死了，手机电也快没了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:170
translate chinese day1_6b17dfbc:

    # ss "Can we go now? "
    ss "现在能走了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:171
translate chinese day1_7d3a0bf0:

    # pc "We can go now. "
    pc "现在可以走了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:172
translate chinese day1_ff13accc:

    # ss "Good, it's almost lunch now and I'm starving! "
    ss "太好了，都快到午饭时间了，我饿坏了！ "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:173
translate chinese day1_0ce5853a:

    # pc "We just had pancakes a couple of hours ago. "
    pc "我们几个小时前才吃过煎饼。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:174
translate chinese day1_8a30bf9e:

    # ss "So? "
    ss "那又怎样？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:175
translate chinese day1_560760f8:

    # pc "Nothing. "
    pc "没什么。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:176
translate chinese day1_8be61208:

    # ss "Let's go get some food. You're buying."
    ss "去吃点东西吧。你请客。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:177
translate chinese day1_6500736f:

    # pc "I barely have any money. "
    pc "我身上几乎没钱了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:178
translate chinese day1_0317c80c:

    # ss "You want to go get a phone too, right? "
    ss "你不是也想买个手机吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:179
translate chinese day1_c1ea7495:

    # pc "Yeah, I kind of need one. "
    pc "是啊，我确实需要一个。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:180
translate chinese day1_0173a82e:

    # ss "And Mom said I had to show you around town too. So you can either buy me lunch, or you can pay for gas. Your choice. "
    ss "而且妈妈说我还得带你逛逛镇上。所以你要么请我吃午饭，要么付油钱。你选吧。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:181
translate chinese day1_896764a5:

    # pc "Fine. But keep it cheap. No steak dinners or anything. "
    pc "行吧。但别太贵。别吃牛排大餐之类的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:183
translate chinese day1_40f90bfb:

    # ss "Yes! I'm craving Jackson Burger. "
    ss "太好了！我正想吃杰克逊汉堡呢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:184
translate chinese day1_2b80e522:

    # pc "Oh yeah! That place is still open? "
    pc "哦对！那家店还开着吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:186
translate chinese day1_7ab998de:

    # ss "Are you kidding? They'll be open forever. Their burgers are the best!"
    ss "开玩笑吗？他们永远都会开着。他们的汉堡是最好的！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:187
translate chinese day1_b99e638f:

    # "I can't argue with that. We used to eat there all the time when I was growing up. "
    "这点我没话可说。 我小时候我们经常去那儿吃。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:188
translate chinese day1_97f399f2:

    # "Every Saturday they have an All-You-Can Eat burger basket. The record holder gets their picture on the wall. I think it was 12 burgers last time I saw. "
    "每个星期六他们都有“汉堡无限量”活动。破纪录的人照片会挂在墙上。我记得上次看到是12个汉堡。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:189
translate chinese day1_3dc69b5e:

    # "I can't tell you how many Saturdays I went there and tried to beat the record, but the most burgers I was ever able to eat was five, and I felt horrible for the rest of the day. "
    "我数不清有多少个星期六我去那里试图打破纪录，但我最多只吃过五个，那天剩下的时间我都感觉糟透了。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:190
translate chinese day1_05aef9a2:

    # pc "Alright, let's go get some burgers then. "
    pc "好吧，那咱们去吃汉堡吧。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:192
translate chinese day1_2adf8f01:

    # ss "Yay! "
    ss "太棒了！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:196
translate chinese day1_8da109e6:

    # "Jackson Burger hasn't changed a bit. It's exactly like I remembered."
    "杰克逊汉堡一点都没变，完全就像我记忆中那样。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:199
translate chinese day1_0c024706:

    # "Except for that picture on the wall with the record holder. The whole time I had come here growing up the record was held by Jessie something, at 12 burgers."
    "除了墙上那张纪录保持者的照片。我小时候每次来这里，纪录都是由一个叫杰西什么的女孩保持的，12个汉堡。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:200
translate chinese day1_e4077616:

    # "Now it's held by somebody named Brandi, at 14 burgers. 14 burgers? HOW? "
    "现在纪录保持者变成了一个叫布兰迪的人，吃了14个汉堡。14个汉堡？怎么可能？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:201
translate chinese day1_485f2732:

    # "Judging by the photo taken, I wonder how she could have even fit that many burgers into her stomach. "
    "看那张照片，我都好奇她怎么能把那么多汉堡塞进肚子里。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:202
translate chinese day1_81e701c9:

    # "She isn't very big. Nice pair of tits though. She doesn't look at all like somebody I would expect to have eaten 14 burgers at Jackson Burger. "
    "她个子并不高大。不过胸挺大。她完全不像那种能在杰克逊汉堡吃下14个汉堡的人。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:205
translate chinese day1_a20a9eeb:

    # "Taking orders is the owner himself, Mr. Jackson, who has been running this place since it opened roughly a hundred years ago."
    "负责点单的是老板本人——杰克逊先生，这家店自大约一百年前开业以来一直由他经营。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:206
translate chinese day1_2b0842e3:

    # "He is in his 70's now, but still sharp, funny, and charismatic."
    "他现在七十多岁了，但头脑依然清醒，风趣幽默，魅力十足。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:208
translate chinese day1_f45be6ca:

    # "I pay for the burgers. The meals are only $5 each, so $10 for the two of us. Such a great deal for these burgers."
    "我付了汉堡的钱。每份餐点只要5美元，所以我们两个人一共10美元。这些汉堡真是物超所值。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:209
translate chinese day1_07b857c3:

    # "Suzy and I sit to eat at one of the small booths that seems as if they haven't changed since the 50's."
    "苏西和我坐在一个小卡座里吃东西，这些卡座看起来好像从50年代起就没变过。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:211
translate chinese day1_d1df107e:

    # ss "So how did registration go? "
    ss "那选课怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:212
translate chinese day1_1e6bd844:

    # pc "Good. I have to take my basics though. "
    pc "挺好的。不过我得选修基础课。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:213
translate chinese day1_82f14014:

    # ss "You haven't taken your basics? "
    ss "你还没选过基础课？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:214
translate chinese day1_a6e674ff:

    # pc "We didn't have to for the college in Brazil. "
    pc "在巴西上大学的时候不用选。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:216
translate chinese day1_b3c6d6c8:

    # ss "Oh God, let me see your schedule. I hope we're not in any of the same classes. "
    ss "天哪，让我看看你的课表。希望我们没有选到任何一门相同的课。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:217
translate chinese day1_c945f9ac:

    # "I hand her the envelope as she wipes her hands on the napkin nearby. "
    "她用旁边的餐巾擦了擦手，我便把信封递给了她。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:224
translate chinese whatswrongclass_e7684331:

    # ss "Are you kidding? I don't need my [brother] watching over everything I do, getting better grades than me, making me look stupid."
    ss "你开玩笑吧？我可不想让那个[brother]时刻盯着我的一举一动，拿比我更好的成绩，让我显得很蠢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:225
translate chinese whatswrongclass_59cc5553:

    # pc "I don't do that."
    pc "我才没那样做。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:226
translate chinese whatswrongclass_f04715ff:

    # ss "Yes you do. You may not try to do it, but you do it. "
    ss "你就是那样。你可能没刻意为之，但你确实做到了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:227
translate chinese whatswrongclass_575e20ff:

    # pc "If I do, I'm sorry."
    pc "如果我真那样了，我很抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:228
translate chinese whatswrongclass_a9df77bb:

    # ss "It's okay. I know you don't mean to. I'm just not as smart as you, I get it."
    ss "没关系。我知道你不是故意的。我只是没你聪明，我懂。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:229
translate chinese whatswrongclass_86e4def6:

    # pc "You are smart though."
    pc "不过你确实很聪明。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:231
translate chinese whatswrongclass_9b60c241:

    # "She raises an eyebrow at me."
    "她挑起眉毛看着我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:232
translate chinese whatswrongclass_f5c9934a:

    # ss "Don't be condescending. We both know I'm not as smart as you. I'm okay with that. I just don't need it pointed out in front of everybody every day. "
    ss "别摆出那种居高临下的态度。我们都知道我没你聪明。我接受这一点。我只是不想每天在大家面前都被这么强调。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:235
translate chinese hopesoclass_aecb5a13:

    # ss "Right? God, could you imagine?"
    ss "对吧？天啊，你能想象吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:239
translate chinese bulletdodged_3fa2b281:

    # ss "Fortunately though, we ARE in some of the same classes, but not at the same times. Bullet dodged."
    ss "不过幸好，我们确实有几门课是重合的，但时间不撞。这下躲过一劫。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:240
translate chinese bulletdodged_df595c4b:

    # "After this we eat mostly in silence."
    "之后我们基本上默默吃完了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:242
translate chinese bulletdodged_60ba3fb6:

    # ss "I'm so damn full. That was delicious."
    ss "我真是撑死了。太好吃了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:243
translate chinese bulletdodged_ba27ea61:

    # "Back when I was younger, I would polish off two or three burgers every time I came here, but now I don't think I could eat another bite."
    "以前我年轻的时候，每次来这里都能吃掉两三个汉堡，但现在我觉得我连一口都吃不下了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:244
translate chinese bulletdodged_b89168a2:

    # "When we are both finished, we head back out to the car."
    "等我们都吃完后，我们便回到车里。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:251
translate chinese touroftown_c7f29f2a:

    # ss "Okay, so quick tour of Skyhill, the town we both know and love. You know where our house and the school are, obviously."
    ss "好，接下来快速逛逛斯凯希尔——这个我们都熟悉且钟爱的镇子。你当然知道我们家和学校在哪儿。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:255
translate chinese touroftown_6df7be13:

    # ss "And Jackson Burger, best burgers in town."
    ss "还有杰克逊汉堡，镇上最好的汉堡。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:257
translate chinese touroftown_02ea2624:

    # ss "Jackson Burger, which we should be eating at right now, is right here. Best burgers in town at a reasonable price that is not too much for you to spend on your [sister]."
    ss "杰克逊汉堡就在这儿，我们本该现在就在那儿吃。镇上最好的汉堡，价格合理，对你来说花这笔钱[sister]也完全负担得起。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:258
translate chinese touroftown_81ebfb9e:

    # ss "Further down the street here, there is the law offices that Mom was talking about. You should stop by there sometime and see about getting a job. "
    ss "沿着这条街再往前走，就是妈妈提过的那个律师事务所。 你应该找个时间去那里看看能不能找份工作。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:261
translate chinese touroftown_d7932580:

    # ss "I've seen a help wanted sign in the window for a long time. Some of my friends said the boss is a bitch, but you're pretty desperate, so you might just have to suck it up and deal with it. "
    ss "我早就看到窗户上贴着招聘启事了。我有些朋友说老板是个泼妇，但你现在挺急的，可能只能咬牙忍一忍了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:264
translate chinese touroftown_7cde6ffc:

    # ss "Then, over here, there is the shopping center. Everything in the town is here basically, starting with the supermarket."
    ss "然后，这边就是购物中心。镇上的东西基本上都在这里，首先是超市。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:267
translate chinese touroftown_6bb210bb:

    # ss "And here's Java Lava, where I work."
    ss "还有这家“Java Lava”，就是我工作的地方。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:273
translate chinese touroftown_fd1c0391:

    # ss "And that's pretty much it. Small boring town. Nothing ever happens. "
    ss "大概就这些了。小地方，挺无聊的。从来没什么事发生。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:274
translate chinese touroftown_ee64d037:

    # pc "Does the Supermarket sell phones?"
    pc "超市里卖手机吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:275
translate chinese touroftown_c3329308:

    # ss "There's a little shop next to it that does. "
    ss "旁边有家小店卖。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:276
translate chinese touroftown_cf36cc17:

    # pc "Could we stop there, and then at the law offices on the way back? "
    pc "我们能先去那儿，回程时再去律师事务所吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:277
translate chinese touroftown_753956bf:

    # ss "Ugh, I guess. "
    ss "唉，行吧。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:280
translate chinese touroftown_b4452e7a:

    # "She parks at the Supermarket and we walk over to the mobile phone store, where I buy the cheapest phone I can find."
    "她把车停在超市，我们走过去那家手机店，我买了能找到的最便宜的手机。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:372
translate chinese tolawoffices_50a16459:

    # "Then she drives to the law office."
    "然后她开车去了律师事务所。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:373
translate chinese tolawoffices_1102de62:

    # ss "I'm staying in the car. Good luck. Don't take too long or I'm going to leave you. "
    ss "我留在车里。祝你好运。别太久，不然我就走了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:375
translate chinese tolawoffices_ae6279f3:

    # "I step out and walk up to the door. How am I supposed to know how long this will take? It isn't really something I can control. "
    "我下了车，走到门口。我怎么知道这要花多长时间？这又不是我能控制的。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:376
translate chinese tolawoffices_3d178aaa:

    # "The glass door has “Law Offices of Mills & Gonzales” printed on it in white lettering. Below that, a printed sign is taped on the inside that says HELP WANTED. "
    "玻璃门上印着白色的“米尔斯与冈萨雷斯律师事务所”字样。门内侧贴着一张打印好的告示，上面写着“招聘”。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:377
translate chinese tolawoffices_2c3a4b71:

    # "I open the door and walk inside. "
    "我推门而入。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:379
translate chinese tolawoffices_810de39d:

    # "The small lobby is decorated with a few potted plants and uncomfortable-looking chairs on the left. "
    "狭小的门厅里摆放着几盆盆栽，左侧是几把看起来不太舒服的椅子。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:380
translate chinese tolawoffices_ae89c21c:

    # "On the right, a large desk sits empty. "
    "右侧，一张大办公桌空无一人。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:381
translate chinese tolawoffices_84b62af0:

    # "A hallway stretches forward some ways, with doors on both sides. "
    "一条走廊向前延伸，两侧分布着几扇门。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:382
translate chinese tolawoffices_c6652712:

    # "The place is empty. Nobody in sight. "
    "这里空无一人，连个人影都没有。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:383
translate chinese tolawoffices_4a165571:

    # pc "Hello? "
    pc "“有人吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:384
translate chinese tolawoffices_614084c5:

    # "I call out. I hear some rustling coming from down the hallway, and a woman's voice calls back. "
    "我喊道。走廊深处传来一阵窸窣声，随后一个女人的声音回应道："

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:385
translate chinese tolawoffices_190db744:

    # "???" "Just a second, I'll be right with you. "
    "???" "“稍等一下，我马上过来。” "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:388
translate chinese tolawoffices_1f90e502:

    # "A frazzled young woman rushes out of the second door on the left, her arms full of papers."
    "一位神色慌张的年轻女子从左侧第二扇门里冲出来，怀里抱着一沓文件。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:389
translate chinese tolawoffices_3f829165:

    # "???" "Can I help you? "
    "???" "有什么可以帮您的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:390
translate chinese tolawoffices_81220faf:

    # pc "I'm here about the Help Wanted poster. "
    pc "我是来看那张招聘启事的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:391
translate chinese tolawoffices_59577895:

    # "???" "Oh really? Great! Let me see if Mrs. Mills has time to see you. "
    "???" "哦，是吗？太好了！我看看米尔斯太太有没有时间见您。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:392
translate chinese tolawoffices_c8235dbf:

    # "???" "Just have a seat over there. "
    "???" "“您先在那边坐会儿。”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:395
translate chinese tolawoffices_430576fd:

    # "I sit down in one of the flimsy chairs as she places the stack of papers onto the desk in the lobby, then turns to rush back down the hall. "
    "我坐在一张单薄的椅子上，她把那沓文件放在大厅的桌子上，随即转身匆匆跑回走廊。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:396
translate chinese tolawoffices_a8e9be7e:

    # "I hear her knock on a door there, and then some muffled conversation as she speaks to who I assume is Mrs. Mills."
    "我听到她在那边敲门，接着传来几句含糊的对话声，我想那应该是米尔斯太太。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:397
translate chinese tolawoffices_4e882efb:

    # "Then she emerges from the hall once again. "
    "随后她又从走廊里走了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:400
translate chinese tolawoffices_26a38581:

    # "???" "Mrs. Mills is on a phone call right now, but she'll be out in a few minutes to speak to you, if you can wait. "
    "???" "米尔斯夫人现在正在打电话，但几分钟后她就会出来见你，如果你能等的话。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:401
translate chinese tolawoffices_8dd934a4:

    # pc "I can wait. "
    pc "我能等。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:404
translate chinese tolawoffices_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/dana_mynameisdana.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_mynameisdana.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:405
translate chinese tolawoffices_d9fe276c:

    # cw "Great! My name is Dana, by the way."
    cw "太好了！顺便说一下，我叫达娜。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:406
translate chinese tolawoffices_3f50a006:

    # pc "I'm [pcname], nice to meet you."
    pc "我叫[pcname]，很高兴见到你。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:407
translate chinese tolawoffices_eb0acbee:

    # cw "Nice to meet you too. "
    cw "我也一样，很高兴认识你。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:409
translate chinese tolawoffices_8ca90698:

    # "We sit in uncomfortable silence for some time. She looks through the stack of papers, dividing them into several piles, while I sit in the chair, looking over a fashion magazine that I have absolutely no interest in. "
    "我们沉默了一会儿，气氛有些尴尬。她翻看着那一沓文件，把它们分成了几堆，而我坐在椅子上，翻看着一本我完全不感兴趣的时尚杂志。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:410
translate chinese tolawoffices_1533650e:

    # cw "So, are you going to school at Skyhill? "
    cw "那么，你是在斯凯希尔上学吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:411
translate chinese tolawoffices_7f11e2c0:

    # pc "I am starting next week. I've been going to a school in Brazil for the last three years, but just moved back to town."
    pc "我下周开始。过去三年我一直在巴西的一所学校上学，但刚搬回镇上。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:412
translate chinese tolawoffices_995f6dc7:

    # cw "Brazil? Wow! How was that? "
    cw "巴西？哇！那儿怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:413
translate chinese tolawoffices_10062577:

    # pc "It was pretty cool. "
    pc "挺不错的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:415
translate chinese tolawoffices_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/dana_wishicouldgetout.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_wishicouldgetout.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:416
translate chinese tolawoffices_97c85be8:

    # cw "I wish I could get out of this town. If I had enough money to leave, I might never come back. "
    cw "真希望我能离开这个小镇。如果我有足够的钱离开，说不定就再也不会回来了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:417
translate chinese tolawoffices_b7827127:

    # "I'm not really sure how to respond to that and before I get a chance to think of what to say, an older woman who I can only assume is Mrs. Mills walks out of the back hall. "
    "我实在不知道该怎么回应，还没来得及想好该说什么，一位我猜想是米尔斯夫人的年长女士就从后厅走了出来。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:419
translate chinese tolawoffices_ff9cb576:

    # "She looks directly at me with piercing blue eyes. She is a petite woman, but her gaze is intimidating, and her stance is almost predatory, like a mountain lion ready to pounce."
    "她那双湛蓝的眼睛直勾勾地盯着我。她个子虽小，但目光却令人胆寒，站姿近乎掠食者，就像一只准备扑击的美洲狮。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:420
translate chinese tolawoffices_f7d5448f:

    # bs "You're here about the job? "
    bs "你是来应聘工作的？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:421
translate chinese tolawoffices_497c698b:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am. "
    pc "是的，女士。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:422
translate chinese tolawoffices_6a65ef6f:

    # bs "Come with me, let's talk in my office. "
    bs "跟我来，到我办公室里谈。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:424
translate chinese tolawoffices_f8aa0aeb:

    # "As I walk past her desk, Dana whispers. "
    "当我从她办公桌旁走过时，达娜低声说道："

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:426
translate chinese tolawoffices_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/dana_goodluck.mp3"
    voice "voices/dana_goodluck.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:427
translate chinese tolawoffices_826f6484:

    # cw "Good luck. "
    cw "“祝你好运。”"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:428
translate chinese tolawoffices_278f313c:

    # "She gives me a smile and I follow Mrs. Mills back to her office at the far end of the hall on the right. "
    "她对我微笑了一下，我便跟在米尔斯夫人身后，走向走廊右侧尽头的办公室。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:430
translate chinese tolawoffices_61b4a885:

    # "Mrs. Mills' office has wood paneled bookshelves fitted into the walls, all filled with law books, small statues, and other little decorative objects. "
    "米尔斯夫人的办公室里，墙壁嵌着木质书架，架上摆满了法律书籍、小雕像和其他装饰品。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:431
translate chinese tolawoffices_6198c9d4:

    # "Two windows behind her desk look out to the green pastures and woods behind the office."
    "办公桌后方的两扇窗户，正对着办公室后面的绿茵草地和树林。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:432
translate chinese tolawoffices_d98a5712:

    # "The rest of her walls are covered with photos of herself shaking hands with people who must be important, along with the various certificates, awards, and accreditations that she had earned over the years. "
    "其余的墙壁上挂满了她与一些想必是重要人物握手的照片，还有她多年来获得的各种证书、奖项和资质认证。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:433
translate chinese tolawoffices_825dbd46:

    # "Her desk is simple and elegant, neatly organized, though there are a few visible coffee stains that hadn't been cleaned up properly."
    "她的办公桌简约而优雅，井井有条，尽管上面有几处没清理干净的咖啡渍。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:434
translate chinese tolawoffices_d6cc5447:

    # "She sits in her desk chair and invites me to sit in one of the wide, padded chairs on the opposite side. "
    "她坐在办公椅上，邀请我坐在对面宽大的软垫椅上。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:437
translate chinese tolawoffices_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/mills_myname.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_myname.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:438
translate chinese tolawoffices_45a20784:

    # bs "My name is Rhonda Mills, half of the Mills and Gonzales Law Firm."
    bs "我叫朗达·米尔斯，是米尔斯与冈萨雷斯律师事务所的合伙人之一。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:439
translate chinese tolawoffices_c38bd46d:

    # bs "The other lawyer who uses these offices is Romero Gonzales, though he is rarely in. "
    bs "另一位共用这间办公室的律师是罗梅罗·冈萨雷斯，不过他很少来。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:440
translate chinese tolawoffices_6650d7d9:

    # bs "The position I'm hiring for is a part-time personal assistant for myself. My previous PA was not able to perform up to my standards and I had to let him go several weeks ago."
    bs "我正在招聘的职位是我的兼职私人助理。我之前的助理没能达到我的标准，几周前我不得不解雇了他。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:441
translate chinese tolawoffices_59a68663:

    # bs "Since then, poor Dana out there has been performing double-duty as both the office secretary and my personal assistant, and she just can't do what I require. "
    bs "从那以后，可怜的达娜一直身兼两职，既要当办公室秘书又要当我的私人助理，但她实在无法满足我的要求。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:442
translate chinese tolawoffices_b33c77d1:

    # bs "I'll be honest with you, we're rather desperate to fill the position at this point. If you are willing to do the job and you can show me that you're not a complete moron, I'll hire you today on a trial basis. "
    bs "老实说，我们现在急需填补这个职位。如果你愿意做这份工作，并且能向我证明你不是个彻头彻尾的蠢货，我今天就试用你。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:443
translate chinese tolawoffices_fa2ab62c:

    # pc "What does the job require? "
    pc "这份工作需要做什么？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:444
translate chinese tolawoffices_6076fe8a:

    # bs "Mostly just running errands for me, keeping track of my calendar, sorting paperwork, answering phones, and cleaning and organizing my office. "
    bs "主要是帮我跑腿、管理我的日程、整理文件、接听电话，以及打扫和整理我的办公室。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:445
translate chinese tolawoffices_a8961c8c:

    # bs "There may be other jobs that pop up from time to time. Your main job will be to do whatever I ask you to do. "
    bs "偶尔可能会有其他临时任务。你的主要职责就是完成我交给你的任何事情。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:446
translate chinese tolawoffices_1ade2b61:

    # pc "I'm going to college, so there are certain times I won't be available. What hours will I be required to work? "
    pc "我正在上大学，所以有些时间我无法在场。我需要工作多长时间？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:447
translate chinese tolawoffices_1dc063b9:

    # bs "We can be accommodating. Come in and work for four hours after you get out of school every weekday, and we'll try to work around special occasions. I understand that school comes first."
    bs "我们可以灵活安排。工作日放学后过来工作四个小时，特殊情况我们会尽量配合。我理解学业是第一位的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:448
translate chinese tolawoffices_c85042ef:

    # pc "What's the pay? "
    pc "工资是多少？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:449
translate chinese tolawoffices_11451a53:

    # bs "Pay is $15 per hour, plus more for special circumstances, such as times where you are needed for specific tasks or events outside of your normal work. "
    bs "时薪为15美元，特殊情况下会额外支付，例如需要你处理常规工作之外的特定任务或活动时。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:450
translate chinese tolawoffices_7e6a396a:

    # pc "What does that mean, exactly? "
    pc "这具体指什么？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:451
translate chinese tolawoffices_7daa25f2:

    # bs "I can't even attempt to predict what I might need you for. There are times that I have a late trial and need a hand carrying things to and from the courtroom, or need somebody to pick up dinner or something. "
    bs "我甚至无法预料我会需要你做什么。有时我会有晚上的庭审，需要有人帮忙搬运法庭往返的物品，或者需要有人去买晚餐之类。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:452
translate chinese tolawoffices_55bb992e:

    # bs "If I ever ask you to work outside of your four hours per weekday, I'll pay you double your normal $15 per hour. "
    bs "如果我要求你在工作日每周四小时之外工作，我会按每小时15美元的两倍支付报酬。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:453
translate chinese tolawoffices_3b775583:

    # pc "Right now, I don't have a car, so I'm not sure that I'd be able to do the errands that the job seems to require. "
    pc "目前我没有车，所以不确定自己能否胜任这份工作似乎需要的跑腿任务。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:454
translate chinese tolawoffices_3277c76a:

    # bs "Oh, that's no problem. If you have a valid driver's license, you can drive one of our cars. We have two spares that we keep for employees. You can even use it away from work for all I care, so long as you sign a waiver that if you crash it, you pay for it. "
    bs "哦，这没问题。只要你有有效的驾照，就可以开我们的车。我们有两辆备用车专门留给员工使用。只要你签个免责声明——如果发生事故由你承担赔偿——我甚至不介意你下班后开去别处。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:455
translate chinese tolawoffices_6d30c765:

    # "It sounds like a great job. Flexible, good pay, and a free car to boot? It seems to fit exactly with what I need right now. "
    "听起来真是份好工作。时间灵活、薪水不错，还免费提供车？这似乎完全符合我目前的需要。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:456
translate chinese tolawoffices_e4988ce7:

    # pc "I'll take the job. "
    pc "我就接受这份工作。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:457
translate chinese tolawoffices_4ef1f9a5:

    # "She holds out her hand and I shake it. "
    "她伸出手，我与她握手。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:461
translate chinese tolawoffices_be90beb5:

    # bs "Great. What's your name again? "
    bs "太好了。你叫什么名字来着？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:462
translate chinese tolawoffices_139c15a3:

    # pc "It's [pcname]. "
    pc "我叫[pcname]。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:463
translate chinese tolawoffices_3bdbf1af:

    # bs "Alright, [pcname], you'll start on Monday. Just come to work immediately after school and plan to work for four hours."
    bs "好的，[pcname]，你周一就开始上班。放学后直接来上班，计划工作四个小时。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:464
translate chinese tolawoffices_67061ba7:

    # bs "Talk to Dana out there to finish up your paperwork and tell her to give you the keys to one of the cars and I'll see you on Monday. "
    bs "去跟那边的达娜说一声，把手续办完，让她把其中一辆车的钥匙给你，周一见。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:465
translate chinese tolawoffices_b2098947:

    # pc "Awesome. Thank you so much. "
    pc "太棒了。非常感谢。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:468
translate chinese tolawoffices_073028be:

    # bs "No, thank you, [pcname]. I look forward to working with you. "
    bs "不，该谢的是我，[pcname]。我很期待和你一起工作。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:469
translate chinese tolawoffices_c18b014a:

    # "Something about the way that she says that and the way her eyes shift downwards only minutely makes me feel a little uncomfortable. "
    "她说话的语气，还有她目光微微向下移的那个小动作，总让我觉得有点不自在。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:470
translate chinese tolawoffices_4dcc6ddc:

    # "I ignore it though, because the job seems to be perfect for me and I walk out to the lobby once again. "
    "不过我没放在心上，因为这份工作似乎非常适合我，于是我再次走向大堂。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:474
translate chinese tolawoffices_4076b1ef:

    # cw "How'd it go? "
    cw "怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:475
translate chinese tolawoffices_cdaafc31:

    # pc "I got the job. "
    pc "我拿到这份工作了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:477
translate chinese tolawoffices_7d7ccea2:

    # cw "Great! It'll be nice to have a new face around here that's my age. Everybody else is so old. "
    cw "太好了！这里能有个和我同龄的新面孔真不错。其他人都太老了。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:478
translate chinese tolawoffices_d302959d:

    # cw "But I didn't say that. "
    cw "但我没说出口。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:479
translate chinese tolawoffices_1faa9126:

    # pc "She told me to have you finish up the paperwork and to give me the keys to one of the cars. "
    pc "她让我让你把手续办完，然后把其中一辆公司的车钥匙交给我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:480
translate chinese tolawoffices_a7184339:

    # cw "Right. I'll get everything ready. "
    cw "好的。我会把一切准备好的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:481
translate chinese tolawoffices_7bb2609c:

    # "It takes about ten more minutes to finish everything up, before Dana hands me the key to one of the company cars. "
    "又花了大约十分钟才把所有事情办完，然后达娜把其中一辆公司车的钥匙交给了我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:482
translate chinese tolawoffices_9ecfa524:

    # cw "You're all set. Looking forward to seeing you on Monday. "
    cw "一切就绪。期待周一见到你。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:483
translate chinese tolawoffices_85047cc8:

    # pc "Thanks Dana. Looking forward to seeing you too. "
    pc "谢谢达娜。我也期待见到你。 "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:484
translate chinese tolawoffices_77431bec:

    # cw "Have a great weekend. "
    cw "周末愉快。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:485
translate chinese tolawoffices_e4ca5b1b:

    # pc "You too. "
    pc "你也是。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:487
translate chinese tolawoffices_08579ad9:

    # "I leave the office and head towards the company car, almost forgetting that Suzy is still waiting for me."
    "我走出办公室走向公司车，差点忘了苏西还在等我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:489
translate chinese tolawoffices_a2ba3c69:

    # ss "Oh my God, it's about time!"
    ss "天哪，你总算来了！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:490
translate chinese tolawoffices_c6cfa804:

    # pc "Hey Suzy. I actually have a ride home now. They gave me one of the company cars. "
    pc "嘿，苏西。其实我现在有车回家了。他们给了我一辆公司车。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:492
translate chinese tolawoffices_9038ef94:

    # ss "What? They gave you a car? "
    ss "什么？他们给你车了？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:493
translate chinese tolawoffices_3e2b0595:

    # pc "Well, just to use while I work here. "
    pc "嗯，只是在这里工作期间用的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:494
translate chinese tolawoffices_305d4eac:

    # ss "Still, that's crazy!"
    ss "不管怎样，这也太疯狂了！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:495
translate chinese tolawoffices_e7c8842f:

    # ss "So they just hired you on the spot? "
    ss "所以他们当场就录用你了？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:496
translate chinese tolawoffices_a76ed944:

    # pc "Yep, I got the job."
    pc "对，我拿到这份工作了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:497
translate chinese tolawoffices_de6bcecf:

    # ss "How? I had like three girlfriends who applied for that same job and never got a call back. "
    ss "怎么可能？我有三个闺蜜也申请了那个职位，结果连个回音都没有。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:498
translate chinese tolawoffices_9a021f76:

    # pc "Really? "
    pc "真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:499
translate chinese tolawoffices_96260a19:

    # ss "Yeah, they said that the woman didn't even seem interested in hiring them. What did you do to get that job? "
    ss "是啊，她们说那个女招聘官看起来根本没兴趣录用她们。你到底是怎么拿到这份工作的？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:500
translate chinese tolawoffices_e9d53d74:

    # pc "Just walked in and asked for it. "
    pc "就直接走进去问的。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:501
translate chinese tolawoffices_7886c317:

    # ss "Didn't perform any favors then? "
    ss "那没做任何好人情吗？ "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:502
translate chinese tolawoffices_1abd5f9d:

    # pc "What? No! Don't be gross. "
    pc "什么？没有！别恶心人。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:503
translate chinese tolawoffices_b2859774:

    # ss "Alright, sure. If you say so. "
    ss "行吧，随你怎么说。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:504
translate chinese tolawoffices_578ec521:

    # "She looks at me suspiciously. "
    "她怀疑地看着我。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:505
translate chinese tolawoffices_31bab525:

    # "I reach into her car and take out my bag that has the cell phone in it. "
    "我伸手进她的车里，拿出了装着手机的包。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:506
translate chinese tolawoffices_ed0d368e:

    # pc "Well, I'll see you at home. Thanks again for driving me around today. "
    pc "那，回家见。今天谢谢你载我到处跑。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:509
translate chinese tolawoffices_65fdee3e:

    # ss "Hey you still owe me gas money!"
    ss "嘿，你还欠我油钱呢！"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:510
translate chinese tolawoffices_e902b56c:

    # pc "Oh yeah, sorry. Will $10 do?"
    pc "哦对，抱歉。10美元够吗？"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:511
translate chinese tolawoffices_87ff94f5:

    # ss "That's fine."
    ss "行。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:513
translate chinese tolawoffices_1b7e7694:

    # "I hand her a ten from the little amount of money I have in my wallet."
    "我从钱包里仅有的零钱里掏出一张十元钞票递给她。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:514
translate chinese tolawoffices_70e27b89:

    # ss "Alright, see you later."
    ss "行，回头见。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:517
translate chinese tolawoffices_98bddef0:

    # ss "Yeah, yeah. See you later. "
    ss "嗯，嗯。回头见。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:520
translate chinese tolawoffices_afba32b7:

    # "She pulls out quickly and cuts off two people as she drives onto the busy road in front of the law offices. "
    "她猛地一踩油门，在驶入律师事务所前那条繁忙的道路时，直接插过了两辆车。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:521
translate chinese tolawoffices_3e9feed9:

    # "I walk over to one of the company cars. They both look exactly the same – generic black sedans, a few years old, with slightly tinted windows."
    "我走向其中一辆公司车。这两辆车看起来一模一样——普通的黑色轿车，开了好几年，车窗稍微贴了点膜。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:522
translate chinese tolawoffices_c65d2d31:

    # "I press the unlock button on the key fob and one of the cars beeps. I open the driver's side door and get inside."
    "我按下钥匙扣上的解锁按钮，其中一辆车发出哔哔声。我打开驾驶座车门，坐了进去。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:525
translate chinese tolawoffices_762489ab:

    # "The inside of the car is clean and smells a bit musty as if it hasn't been used for a while."
    "车内很干净，但有一股霉味，好像很久没开过一样。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:526
translate chinese tolawoffices_76a7ccb7:

    # "It is simple and not very flashy, but it will get me around until I can buy a car of my own."
    "车内装潢简朴，没什么花哨的地方，不过在我买得起自己的车之前，它能满足我的出行需求。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:527
translate chinese tolawoffices_07e0ebfc:

    # "Actually, it is probably better than any car that I'd ever owned. I'd only had one car before - an old junker that my dad had gotten me."
    "其实，这车恐怕比我以前开过的任何车都要好。我之前只拥有一辆车——那是我爸给我弄来的一辆老破车。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:528
translate chinese tolawoffices_ff0881b6:

    # "It barely ran and needed constant work. I sold it off before going to Brazil. Then down there, I didn't have any form of transportation. I just walked everywhere. "
    "那车勉强能跑，还得时常修理。去巴西之前我就把它卖了。到了那里，我没有任何交通工具，只能到处步行。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:529
translate chinese tolawoffices_076df576:

    # "The car starts as soon as I turn the key, and once I back out onto the street it drives perfectly fine. It doesn't have much power, but enough to get me from place to place."
    "我一转动钥匙，车就发动了，倒车驶上街道后，行驶起来也完全没问题。 虽然动力不大，但足够带我四处奔波。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:530
translate chinese tolawoffices_61f7e0fb:

    # "I would have taken the job even without the car, but now, not having to rely on somebody else to drive me around is the best feeling. "
    "就算没有这辆车，我也会接受这份工作，但现在，不用再依赖别人开车接送，这种感觉真是太棒了。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:531
translate chinese tolawoffices_5ba209a0:

    # "It's evening now. I have a little time left to do some things before heading home for the night, and I have the means to go anywhere I want."
    "现在是傍晚。在回家过夜之前，我还有一点时间可以做些事情，而且我有能力去任何我想去的地方。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:532
translate chinese tolawoffices_f228727e:

    # "I suddenly remember the park that I used to play at when I was younger and I wonder what it looks like now."
    "我突然想起小时候常去的那座公园，好奇它现在是什么样子。"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:533
translate chinese tolawoffices_cfe242e6:

    # "There are plenty of places to go, and I have plenty of time to check out that park later. Where do I want to go NOW?"
    "可去的地方多着呢，等会儿我有大把时间去看看那座公园。但此刻，我想去哪里呢？"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:219
    old "What's wrong with us being in the same class?"
    new "我们同班有什么问题吗？"

    # game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:221
    old "I hope so too. That would be horrible."
    new "我也希望如此。那样可太糟糕了。"

